com.compendium.io.jabber
Class BSPresencesOfJID

java.lang.Object
  com.compendium.io.jabber.BSPresencesOfJID

public class BSPresencesOfJID
extends java.lang.Object

BSPresencesOfJID contains presence information about all resources the given JID is logged from. It includes list BSPresenceInfo records.

Author:
Jiri Komzak, Knowledge Media Institute, Open University, United Kingdom
